│  62     PPC_FP128TyID, ///< 128-bit floating point type (two 64-bits,       │
│ PowerPC)                                                                    │
│  63     VoidTyID,      ///< type with no size                               │
│  64     LabelTyID,     ///< Labels                                          │
│  65     MetadataTyID,  ///< Metadata                                        │
